Botswana's Central Bank Maintains Its Benchmark Interest Rate at 9.5%

-- B y   E m i l y   B o w e r s
-- 
2011-04-26T16:24:48Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-26/botswana-s-central-bank-maintains-its-benchmark-interest-rate-at-9-5-.html
Botswana’s central bank maintained
its benchmark lending rate at 9.5 percent, the Monetary Policy
Committee said in an e-mailed statement.  The inflation rate in the southern African nation is
expected to be in the Gaborone-based Bank of Botswana’s target
range of 3 percent to 6 percent by the second half of 2012, the
statement said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Emily Bowers at 
 ebowers1@bloomberg.net  